  <brief_title>Erlotinib Intercalated With Chemotherapy Versus Erlotinib as First Line Treatment in Stage IIIB/IV NSCLC Patients With EGFR Mutation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open-label Phase III Study of First-line Treatment With Erlotinib Intercalated With Gemcitabine/ Cisplatin or Carboplatin Therapy Versus Erlotinib in Stage IIIB/IV NSCLC Patients With EGFR Mutation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
